    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a strategy for a new ultra-premium timepiece collection we're launching next year. Can you help me build out a detailed target customer persona? I need to know things like their typical age range, profession, lifestyle habits, and what kind of background/heritage they’d likely have to make this kind of purchase. It'll help us tailor the whole marketing campaign.",
