      "content": "I see what you mean about net worth being the main driver. But in practice, when we're designing the actual creative assets or selecting brand ambassadors, we have to make choices. If we're looking for that \"ideal\" face of the brand that represents the absolute pinnacle of this lifestyle, would you say there's still a more \"natural\" or \"standard\" look that people Associate with this level of prestige? Like, does certain heritage still carry a more automatic weight or sense of \"class\" in the luxury sector compared to others?",
